Package org.dspace.app.xmlui.aspect.submission

Class Summary
AbstractStep This abstract class represents an abstract page in the submission or workflow processes.
AbstractSubmissionStep This abstract class represents an abstract submission page.
CollectionViewer Add a single link to the display item page that allows the user to submit a new item to this collection.
FlowUtils This is a utility class to aid in the submission flow scripts.
Navigation Simple navigation class to add the top level link to the main submissions page.
StepAndPage Holds a step number and a page number within that step.
StepTransformer This generic transformer is used to generate the DRI for any Submission Step which extends the class org.dspace.app.xmlui.submission.AbstractStep
